                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270215-199-victim1094 t18270215-199-viclabel1075"></join>. On the 29th of January the prisoner came and bought a pair of ties, which came to 2d.; I missed a bundle off the counter, and followed him - he denied having them; I found them under his arm.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270215-199-person1095">
